title: Eccentric Neighbor
description:
Written by Kristy Lopez-Bernal
Starring: Lisa Kleinman, Jonathan Marballi, Langan Kingsley, Jon Bershad, Kerry O'Brien, Michael Kloos, Kristy Lopez-Bernal, Avery Monsen, Dan Hodapp

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, June 3, 2013.

Filmed by Tom Levin, Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
